<HEADLINE> Karlsruhe Advances in UEFA Cup </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NICOSIA, September 30 (Xinhua) -- Karlsruhe SC of Garmany tied
Anorthosis Famagusta of Cyprus 1-1 in Larnaca, Cyprus, on Tuesday
to advanced in the second round of the UEFA Cup.
</P>
<P>
The Germans had won the first leg of the first round matchup at
home of Karlsruhe.
</P>
<P>
Anorthosis squandered several excellent opportunities to score
but its star forward, Vesco Mihailovic managed to open the score
in the 13th minute with a powerful drive into the righthand corner
of the goal.
</P>
<P>
The equalizer came from Guenther Schepens in the 41st minute
when he came face to face with the Anorthosis goalie and beat him
easily with a shot high into the left corner of the net.  
</P>
</TEXT>
