people. The program adopted by the congress and the new Central
Committee elected by the congress will lead all Chinese people to
march into the 21-st century, he noted.
</P>
<P>
He also praised the friendship between China and Uganda in
various fields in the past 35 years since China and Uganda
established diplomatic relations.
</P>
<P>
On behalf of the Ugandan government and people, Rebecca
Kadaga, state minister of the Foreign Ministry, congratulated
Chinese people on the smooth return of Hong Kong, and wished more
fruitful development of friedship between the two countries.
</P>
<P>
More than 300 guests including Jovino Ayumu Akaki, state
minister in the Ministry of Land, Housing and Urban Development,
Kampala-based diplomats and representatives of Chinese
institutions and companies and immigrants were present on the
occasion.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, Chinese embassies to Ethiopia, Eritrea, Mozambique,
Tanzania and other African countries also held receptions for the
celebrations of the 48th anniversary of the founding of the
People's Republic of China.
</P>
