government officials, including Chief Secretary for Administration
Anson Chan and Financial Secretary Donald Tsang Yam-kuen, Chief
Justice of the Final Appeal Court Andrew Li, President of the
Provisional Legislative Council Rita Fan, and personalities of
various circles.  
