<HEADLINE> Australian Dollar Closes Stronger </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, October 1 (Xinhua) -- The Australian dollar sailed to
a stronger close today, blown along by a sudden jump up in the
gold price overnight.
</P>
<P>
