<HEADLINE> Johannesburg to Host Africa's Biggest Art </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, October 1 (Xinhua) -- A grand international
exhibition of contemporary art exhibition, the Biennale, is to be
held in Johannesburg, South Africa's economic capital, from
October 12, organizers of the exhibition said.
</P>
<P>
