Bulgaria's National Assembly Chairman Jordan Sokolov and Justice
Minister Vasil Gotsev, and the Czech Republic's Chamber of
Deputies Chairman Milos Zeman and Deputy Premier and Foreign
Minister Josef Zieleniec. 
